{"tid":89171,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 韓星當兵問題","createTime":"2017-01-21T07:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T07:41:32.000Z","uid":58285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cec9dd9184416179df7b3702facea4318b5f684","tid":89171,"uid":58285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"依幾日因為要寫文，扒左好多關於韓國男星當兵嘅生活，韓國軍隊嘅虐兵同大蝦細問題好似都幾嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁啲明星入伍咪應該會俾人蝦得特別緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地嘅名氣，加上咁多粉絲寄野俾佢地，一定大把葡萄佢地嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但上網又唔多揾到有韓星服役被虐，宋仲基果啲仲好似當得好開心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係佢地收得密定真係無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 非哈韓，對韓星幾乎零認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52c69f610f54dd72c0e79edfe0b723dede811d9","tid":89171,"uid":2172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:34:54.000Z","msg":"因為好多韓星都係做演藝兵，無前線咁辛苦。係近幾年因為成日犯軍規先廢演藝兵制度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：仇泡"},{"pid":"c7e6662680cef1888dadeb59cdd409c3f6239e92","tid":89171,"uid":58285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為好多韓星都係做演藝兵，無前線咁辛苦。係近幾年因為成日犯軍規先廢演藝兵制度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：仇泡</blockquote><br />\n好似從2015年廢左，宋仲基就係第一個廢左文藝兵之後做一般軍人嘅藝人，但好似依兩年都無聽講過佢地俾人蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔信佢地無特別待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:非宋仲基粉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係上網成日睇到好多佢嘅資料所以成日講佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}